nodes.description: The 컴퓨터공학부, part of 한성대학교, is responsible for managing 서면신청, which includes overseeing the course registration process for graduating students, students in their extended semesters, and transfer students. This department plays a crucial role in ensuring that these specific groups of students can successfully navigate their academic requirements and registration procedures. Additionally, the 컴퓨터공학부 is specifically tasked with the management of 서면신청, further emphasizing its importance in facilitating the academic journey of these students.

The "2025-1 컴퓨터공학부 1차 서면신청 메뉴얼" is a comprehensive guide detailing the written application procedures for the Computer Engineering Department for the first semester of 2025. This manual serves to inform students about the necessary steps and requirements involved in the written application process for that academic term.

The entity "서면신청 유의사항" refers to important considerations that must be taken into account when submitting a written application. This includes a comprehensive overview of the necessary precautions and guidelines that should be followed during the written application process. The descriptions emphasize the significance of being aware of these key points to ensure a successful submission.

구글폼은 서면신청을 위한 온라인 제출 양식으로 사용되는 도구이다.

The "컴퓨터공학부 행정사무실" is responsible for the administrative tasks of the Computer Engineering Department. This office handles various administrative duties, including inquiries related to written applications.
서면 신청 시 교수님 승인 메일을 캡쳐하는 방법에 대한 설명. 이 내용은 2025-1 컴퓨터공학부 1차 서면신청 메뉴얼 문서에서 추출함. 3페이지에 위치함.

The "수강신청원" is a form used for course registration, specifically designed for students to fill out when applying for classes. It serves as an official document required for the course enrollment process.

The entity "분반" refers to the information that indicates the division of classes for each subject. It encompasses the categorization of classes for various courses, providing a clear distinction between different sections or groups within the same subject.

지원자가 기재해야 하는 연락처
The term "이메일" refers to the personal email address that must be provided in an application. It is the email address that the applicant is required to include in their submission.
The term "주소" refers to the address that an individual is required to provide in their application. It signifies the specific location that applicants must include in their submitted documents.

The term "소속" refers to the institution or organization that an individual must indicate on their application. It encompasses the school, major, and year of study that the applicant is required to provide.

On March 7th, it is the second deadline for written applications related to course registration adjustments. Applications must be submitted by 1 PM on this date. This information has been extracted from documents concerning course registration and is located on the relevant page.
The entity "서면신청 가능 여부" refers to the status of whether written applications are permissible. It encompasses information that indicates whether such written applications can be submitted.

The entity "수강정정" refers to the process of course registration correction. It encompasses guidance on how to amend course registrations, including the procedures and relevant announcements associated with this process. The first correction period for course registration allows all students to make changes on February 14th (Friday) from 11:00 AM to 2:50 PM. Additionally, from 3:00 PM to 6:00 PM, students have the option to switch between day and evening classes. This information has been extracted from documents related to course registration and is located on the relevant page.

The "컴퓨터공학부 행정 사무실" is responsible for handling administrative tasks related to the Computer Engineering Department. This office manages inquiries related to course registration and oversees various administrative functions within the department.
